title: Tryouts for Newton Select Teams Tuesday
text:
Tryouts for Newton Select Teams Tuesday Published: Friday, Oct. 23, 2015 11:17 a.m. CDT By Newton Daily News 
Tryouts for Newton Select Traveling Basketball Teams are Tuesday at Newton High School. These are youth teams for girls and boys from fourth grade through eighth grade. 
Registration is $180 to participate with half of the fee payable Tuesday and the other half by Dec. 31. 
Registration and check-in begins at 4:45 p.m. at the NHS cafeteria. 
The tryouts for the boys’ fourth-fifth grade team and the sixth-seventh grade team are from 5:45 to 6:45 p.m. Tuesday in the NHS lower gym. The eighth-grade boys’ team tryouts are from 8 to 9 p.m. in the NHS upper gym. 
For girls, tryouts for the fourth-sixth grade team are 5:45 to 6:45 p.m. in the upper gym. 
The seventh-eighth grade team tryouts are from 6:45 to 7:45 p.m. to upper gym. 
At 5:30 p.m., immediately following registration, a welcoming event will take place in the high school cafeteria for parents of players trying out. 
This meeting will provide information needed so parents know what is happening during their child’s tryout. 
Parents are invited to wait in the commons (coffee provided) until their child’s tryout is over. Parents will not be allowed in the gymnasiums during the tryout process. 
Practices begin in Novemenber
